trans-unit.source: Represents an event that an instance store raises to notify hosts about a condition.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un evento generato da un archivio di istanze per segnalare agli host una condizione.

trans-unit.source: Examples: <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasRunnableWorkflowEvent" /> and <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasActivatableWorkflowEvent" />.
trans-unit.target: Esempi: <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasRunnableWorkflowEvent" /> e <see cref="T:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.HasActivatableWorkflowEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: Compares two instances of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Confronta due istanze degli oggetti <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: The object to be compared with the current object.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto da confrontare con l'oggetto corrente.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object and the passed object converted as the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> are the same.
trans-unit.target: Determina se l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> corrente e l'oggetto passato convertito come <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> sono uguali.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="True" /> if the objects are same; otherwise, returns <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce <see langword="True" /> se gli oggetti sono uguali. In caso contrario, <see langword="False" />.

trans-unit.source: The object to be compared with the current object.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto da confrontare con l'oggetto corrente.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object and the passed <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object are the same.
trans-unit.target: Determina se l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> corrente e l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> passato sono uguali.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="True" /> if the objects are same; otherwise, returns <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce <see langword="True" /> se gli oggetti sono uguali. In caso contrario, <see langword="False" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce il codice hash per l'istanza di <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: The hash code for the instance.
trans-unit.target: Codice hash dell'istanza.

trans-unit.source: Returns the XName (namespace combined with name) of the persistence event.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce l'oggetto XName (spazio dei nomi combinato con il nome) dell'evento di persistenza.

trans-unit.source: XName of the persistence event
trans-unit.target: XName dell'evento di persistenza

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: Primo oggetto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> da confrontare.

trans-unit.source: The second <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: Secondo oggetto da confrontare <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects are the same.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce un valore che indica se gli oggetti <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> specificati sono uguali.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the two objects are the same; otherwise, <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="True" /> se i due oggetti sono uguali; in caso contrario, <see langword="False" />.

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: Primo oggetto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> da confrontare.

trans-unit.source: The second <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> object to compare.
trans-unit.target: Secondo oggetto da confrontare <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> objects are not the same.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce un valore che indica se gli oggetti <see cref="T:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceEvent" /> specificati non sono uguali.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the two objects are the same; otherwise, <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="True" /> se i due oggetti sono uguali; in caso contrario, <see langword="False" />.
